
  Meditite    Fighting Type Pokémon

  MEDITITE undertakes rigorous 
  mental training deep in the mountains. 
   However, whenever it meditates, 
  Meditite always loses its 
  concentration and focus.  As 
  a result, its training never 
  ends. 
	Evolution Chain
      Meditite ► Medicham

