 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Pure-power:

    This Pokémon's Attack is doubled 
  in battle.

  This bonus does not count as 
  a stat modifier.

  This ability functions identically 
  to huge power.

  Telepathy:

    This Pokémon does not take 
  damage from friendly Pokémon's 
  moves, including single-target 
  moves aimed at it.


